Package: metathresholds
Type: Package
Title: Applies thresholds to classified metagenomics data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sarah", "Buddle", "sarah.buddle.21@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4738-9469"))
Description: Takes output of common taxonomic classifiers such as Kraken2 and
    applies thresholds based on raw reads, reads per million ratio and proportion
    of microbial reads.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
